995
1:25:27,135 --> 1:25:41,55
You know you always
got a job with me, right?


996
1:25:41,55 --> 1:25:47,22
Hey, bitch!


997
1:25:47,22 --> 1:25:59,334
Motherfucker, l'm tired of your ass!


998
1:25:59,334 --> 1:26:3,438
What's up, boss, my man?
l heard you was out.


999
1:26:3,438 --> 1:26:6,441
Didn't even try to contact me?
What's up with that?


1000
1:26:6,441 --> 1:26:9,344
l heard you squaring up on me.


1001
1:26:9,344 --> 1:26:11,446
How your job search?


1002
1:26:11,446 --> 1:26:16,51
-lt's all right.
